      "type": "string",
      "description": "When set this asset will inherit properties from the named asset.\n\nWhen inheriting from another MovementConfig most properties will simply be copied from the parent asset to this asset. In the case where both child and parent provide a field the child field will simply replace the value provided by the parent, in the case of nested structures this will apply to the fields within the structure. In some cases the field may decide to act differently, for example: by merging the parent and child fields together.",
